{"tid":2182320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記得踴躍登記普及社區檢測計劃","createTime":"2020-08-31T08:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T08:35:35.000Z","uid":226913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f55dc19da01082b8457337507d76ee33a15d16b","tid":2182320,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:35:35.000Z","msg":"作為良好市民，參與普及社區檢測計劃係我地嘅責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n登記過程非常簡單，只需要提供身份證號碼同電話，再選擇地點同時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.communitytest.gov.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr06npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=45dd9155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.communitytest.gov.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyzM2ra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyzM2ra.jpg&h=522a3c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjATHrP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjATHrP.jpg&h=3cf56b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得<span class=\"red\">千祈唔好</span>填錯身份證號碼，亦<span class=\"red\">千祈唔好</span>登記超過一次，如果搞到有需要嘅人少咗個機會就真係唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}